a-4e5c-845b-d662222574c0.jpg?1782749061"}], "mechanics_snippets": [], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/e/8e68aa29-9f38-48a2-b00a-39aef9d91f6d.jpg?1782721038", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/e/8e68aa29-9f38-48a2-b00a-39aef9d91f6d.jpg?1782721038", "card": "Dwarven Thaumaturgist"}}